premise_source_doc_sentence: The 2016 NBA Finals was the championship series of the National Basketball Association  (  NBA  )  2015 -- 16 season and conclusion of the 2016 playoffs .

Prior to the 2016 NBA Finals , when the Cleveland Cavaliers overcame the Golden State Warriors , and the 2014 NBA Finals when the San Antonio Spurs bested the Miami Heat , the Pistons were the last Finals champion to have been runner-up to the same opponent the previous season as they did in the 1988 Finals .
Before the Cleveland Cavaliers ' Game 7 win at Golden State in the 2016 NBA Finals , this was the last time a road team had won Game 7 in the NBA Finals .

The 2016 NBA Finals of the Cleveland Cavaliers and Golden State Warriors rematch was the most watched NBA Final series on ABC with an average of 20.28 million viewers , but only averaged an 11.4 rating / 21 share .

Game 7 of the 2016 NBA Finals registered the network 's highest rated and most watched NBA game with an average 15.8 rating / 29 share and 31.02 million viewers while peaking with a whopping 22.5 rating / ~ 41 share and 44.51 million viewers in the last 10 minutes of the game .
